snippet.title: Amber Heard kept a tight grip on husband Johnny Depp after they partied together at his Rock in Rio
snippet.description:
He took to the stage to perform with super-band the Hollywood Vampires at Rock and Rio on Thursday night.
And while the audience was adorned with Johnny Depp fans, it looked as though none could compare to the 52-year-old's smitten wife, Amber Heard. 
The 29-year-old actress was on hand to support her man at the gig, which saw him play alongside the likes of Alice Cooper, Aerosmith's Joe Perry, Guns N' Roses' Duff McKagan, and Bruce Witkin
